{"type": "article", "id": 18430, "title": "植物灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-03T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134745bct9mjMUuhHsiQPY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些种在灯光下面的植物，也许是想最大化利用光照。白色的环状灯罩有一种温暖的感觉，LED 灯光在内侧，使光线直接照射在植物上面。下面有个凹槽放一些种子，只需浇水就可生长而完全不需要土壤。绿色的植物点缀在其中，填补了环形灯中的空隙，有一种在温室里的被保护的感觉。这盏灯正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/224399175/grasslamp-the-modern-desktop-garden?ref=video\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134743KPFLEkyRZmH1bdqp.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"656\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6247619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134743fC9HoWM0p2kX786K.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"666\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134744oufOqHLSkcitxD0B.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"656\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6247619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134744gvXSpJrGiZACyIxu.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"656\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6247619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}